{
  "stem": "5644.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only holding the gun, or holding the machine gun, and training and telling us how and what to do.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We been trained, mostly, if the killing have to come, knifes, wires, and bayonets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, in some cases, the helmet which is wearing on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We been trained how to kill him with his own helmet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When you pull a helmet back from his head, from the back, the band around is choking you to death.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No man is-- you see, I was a boy of 19, 20, 21, 22-- I'd say young people were not taking the way I'm thinking now.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because now, in my opinion, I would like to see some danger things, how to survive, not how to fight.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at that time, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My enemy, mine-- my thig what happened to my people, the Germans, I crossed off a matter of fact after once writing Nazis.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not calling it Nazis.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm calling Germans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To me, the word Nazis is nonexistent, practically.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I got it in my speech, the first run, because, I, in my book, the whole German nation is guilty.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not Nazis.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can't see any Nazis, because the, the, the thing which happen to Hitler in the end of the war was only one, and the end of the war, not one German went against it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I haven't seen him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I haven't heard about them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "To me, those are Germans, not Nazis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As Germans, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, look.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What someone would said no, one or two, whatever-- no, but I seen, I, I have heard, that Stroop, Stroop, which was liquidizing the ghetto, took something, and he got in his report that they did have there Wehrmacht fighting the Jews in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
